========================================================================
FLORES-200 modern-register replication of the Bible language tree
========================================================================

Matched 55/57 Bible languages to FLORES (by ISO 639-3 + script).
Dropped 2 (no modern FLORES counterpart):
    - Latin: no FLORES file for iso 'lat'
    - Syriac: no FLORES file for iso 'syr'
Script mismatches (2) — Bible vs FLORES use different scripts, so the RAW
arm is not a same-script control for these (the romanized/IPA arm removes this); romanized arm is clean:
    - Icelandic: Bible Ethiopic vs FLORES Latn
    - Serbian: Bible Latin vs FLORES Cyrl

Gold tree: 55 languages across 13 families (same gold scores BOTH corpora).
Bible: 2000 verse-aligned verses/lang (<= 30k chars).
FLORES: 2009 sentences/lang (dev+devtest); RAW arm capped to 30000 chars/lang to match the Bible budget.
  sparse FLORES languages (K/N>0.30 -> noisy trigram distance, interpret with care):
    Mandarin_Chinese: K/N=0.84
    Japanese: K/N=0.66
    Korean: K/N=0.56
    Amharic: K/N=0.41
    Thai: K/N=0.31

